<BaseLayout
  title="6-Layer PCB Engineering Guide | Signal Integrity, Sequential Lamination & Stackup Design | XFPCB"
  description="Engineering consultation for 6-layer PCBs: signal integrity analysis, sequential lamination process, via architecture (through/buried/microvia), stackup selection with 3 architectures, DFM rules for layer registration, and 4-layer vs 6-layer cross-comparison. XFPCB China."
  keywords="6 layer PCB signal integrity, 6 layer PCB sequential lamination, 6 layer PCB stackup design, buried via PCB, microvia PCB, 6 layer PCB DFM, 4 layer vs 6 layer PCB, PCB layer registration, 6 layer PCB manufacturer, XFPCB"
  canonical="https://xfpcb.com/products/6-layer-pcb/"
  ogTitle="6-Layer PCB Engineering Guide | Signal Integrity, Sequential Lamination & Stackup Design | XFPCB"
  ogDescription="Engineering consultation for 6-layer PCBs: signal integrity analysis, sequential lamination process, via architecture (through/buried/microvia), stackup selection with 3 architectures, and DFM rules for layer registration."
